洛德在给粉丝的感人信中表示，她“再次生活在心碎之中” https://www.nme.com/news/music/lorde-says-shes-living-in-heartbreak-again-in-emotional-letter-to-fans-3501612?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=lorde-says-她再次生活在伤心中给粉丝的情感信Tom SkinnerThu, 21 Sep 2023 07:39:36 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3501612 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/LORDE_PYRAMID_SUNDAY_PHOEBEFOX-22-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="洛德现场表演" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/LORDE_PYRAMID_SUNDAY_PHOEBEFOX-22-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/LORDE_PYRAMID_SUNDAY_PHOEBEFOX-22-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/LORDE_PYRAMID_SUNDAY_PHOEBEFOX-22-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/LORDE_PYRAMID_SUNDAY_PHOEBEFOX-22-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/LORDE_PYRAMID_SUNDAY_PHOEBEFOX-22-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/LORDE_PYRAMID_SUNDAY_PHOEBEFOX-22-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位歌手还表示她正在处理一些健康问题</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lorde-says-shes-living-in-heartbreak-again-in-emotional-letter-to-fans-3501612">洛德在致粉丝的感人信中称她“再次生活在心碎之中”，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/LORDE_PYRAMID_SUNDAY_PHOEBEFOX-22-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="洛德现场表演" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/LORDE_PYRAMID_SUNDAY_PHOEBEFOX-22-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/LORDE_PYRAMID_SUNDAY_PHOEBEFOX-22-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/LORDE_PYRAMID_SUNDAY_PHOEBEFOX-22-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/LORDE_PYRAMID_SUNDAY_PHOEBEFOX-22-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/LORDE_PYRAMID_SUNDAY_PHOEBEFOX-22-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/LORDE_PYRAMID_SUNDAY_PHOEBEFOX-22-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lorde">洛德</a>在给粉丝的一封感人的信中讲述了她目前如何“生活在心碎中”。</p><p>这位新西兰流行歌星在电子邮件的开头解释说，她在伦敦，自五月以来一直在那里生活和工作。 “这里的事情感觉很清楚，”她继续说道。 “我没见过多少朋友；大多数时候，我都是独自思考。”</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/lordes-new-live-show-solar-power-3479935">洛德大胆的现场回归展现了截然不同的篇章</a></strong></li></ul><p>洛德补充道：“我去游泳，去上班，步行回家或乘火车，在厨房吃饭，上床睡觉时想着我正在做的事情。我开始想念我的朋友和家人，就像我缺乏维生素一样。”</p><p>后来，这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/lorde-solar-power-review-3023597">《太阳能》</a>歌手说她“再次生活在心碎之中”——将这种感觉描述为“不同但相同”。</p><p> “我总是感到疼痛，我忘记了原因，然后又想起来了，”洛德继续说道。 “我并不是想逃避痛苦，我现在明白了，痛苦并不是什么可以逃避的事情，与它一起前进实际上是非常美丽的。但有时我厌倦了和自己在一起。</p><p> “我吃巧克力是为了尝试控制内啡肽，带回复活节早晨的甜蜜幸福。我坐在时间机器里等待它运转，但它还没有被发明出来。”</p><p>洛德随后向她的粉丝讲述了她目前遇到的一些健康问题，并表示“[她的]身体真的发炎了”。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">洛德在给粉丝的新电子邮件中分享了她的感受：</p><p> “我又生活在心碎之中。这是不同的，但也是一样的。我总是感到疼痛，忘记了原因，然后又想起来了。我不是想逃避痛苦，我现在明白痛苦不是可以逃避的，有…… <a href="https://t.co/kT7Q6LAGsl">pic.twitter.com/kT7Q6LAGsl</a></p><p> - Pop Base (@PopBase) <a href="https://twitter.com/PopBase/status/1704654419948929390?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 9 月 21 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>她继续说道：“我的肠道功能不正常，我的皮肤比以前更糟糕，我已经生过六次病了。今年早些时候，我意识到倾听自己身体的声音对我来说很难，这是我从未真正学会如何去做的事情。</p><p> “今年我一直在努力教会自己这一点，但实际上这很困难，相当有挑战性，让我充分意识到我每次都忽视它或没有给它所需要的东西，因为打架而羞辱它或飞行反应，服用了一把药片并坚持了下来。”</p><p>洛德在信中的其他地方说，她创作音乐的原因是“因为我需要”。 “歌曲是咒语；释放某物的咒语，打开门的咒语，”她写道。 “每次我把看到的东西用文字表达出来，并配上合适的音乐，我心里的一个结就会松动。但面对结也很痛。”</p><p>您可以在上面的帖子中看到电子邮件的摘录。 </p><figure id="attachment_3481991" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3481991" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3481991" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/lorde@2000x1270.jpg" alt="洛德在舞台上现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/lorde@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/lorde@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/lorde@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/lorde@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/lorde@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/lorde@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3481991" class="wp-caption-text">洛德现场表演。图片来源：Joseph Okpako/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>上个月，Lorde 在 Boardmasters 2023 上表演了<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/lordes-new-live-show-solar-power-3479935">新的“夜视”节目</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lorde-two-new-songs-live-boardmasters-festival-2023-3481990">并在那里首次亮相了两首新歌</a>。她还在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-lorde-perform-green-light-with-caroline-polacheck-at-sziget-festival-2023-3482999">Sziget</a>和 Øya 等各种欧洲音乐节上进行了现场表演。</p><p>后者演出结束后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lorde-promises-to-show-light-on-inside-me-to-fans-soon-as-she-teases-return-3481068">洛德在 Instagram 上分享了有关她最新舞台表演的神秘更新</a>。 “不，这不是任何事情的开始，”她写道，“只是想让你知道我内心有一盏灯……很快就会向你展示。”</p><p>早在三月份，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lorde-teases-fans-about-new-music-3421840">洛德就暗示她可能正在创作新音乐</a>，但表示她“不会透露，暂时不会”。上个月，她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lorde-shares-update-on-writing-process-for-next-album-i-dont-want-to-wait-3398853">告诉歌迷她“对即将发生的事情感到兴奋”</a> ，并且她说她的下一张专辑将会尽早推出。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lorde-says-shes-living-in-heartbreak-again-in-emotional-letter-to-fans-3501612">洛德在致粉丝的感人信中称她“再次生活在心碎之中”，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
 《性教育》为何结束？ https://www.nme.com/news/tv/why-is-sex-education-ending-netflix-3501275?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=why-is-sex-education-ending-netflixAdam Starkey Thu, 21 Sep 2023 07:01:54 +0000 NewsTV NewsNetflixSex Education https://www.nme.com/?p=3501275 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sex-Education-season-4-main-new.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="性教育第四季" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sex-Education-season-4-main-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sex-Education-season-4-main-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sex-Education-season-4-main-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sex-Education-season-4-main-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sex-Education-season-4-main-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sex-Education-season-4-main-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>第四季也是最后一季于 9 月登陆 Netflix</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/why-is-sex-education-ending-netflix-3501275">为什么“性教育”结束了？</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sex-Education-season-4-main-new.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="性教育第四季" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sex-Education-season-4-main-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sex-Education-season-4-main-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sex-Education-season-4-main-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sex-Education-season-4-main-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sex-Education-season-4-main-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sex-Education-season-4-main-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/sex-education"><em>《性教育》</em></a>第四季已正式完结。</p><p>这部<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a>喜剧由劳里·纳恩 (Laurie Nunn) 创作，讲述了莫代尔中学学生、教师和家长的生活，奥蒂斯（阿萨·巴特菲尔德饰）和梅芙（艾玛·麦基饰）在那里设立了一家性诊所，帮助其他人解决性问题。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/sex-education-season-3-review-3047830">《性教育》第三季评论：角色太多，时间太少</a></strong></li></ul><p>该剧第三季荣获 2022 年艾美奖最佳喜剧系列奖。饰演艾米·吉布斯的艾米·卢·伍德 (Aimee Lou Wood) 还获得了英国电影学院奖最佳女喜剧表演奖。</p><h2>为什么<em>《性爱自修室》</em>第四季就完结了？ </h2><figure id="attachment_3501198" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3501198" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3501198" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sex_Education_Season_4_Ncuti_Gatwa.jpg" alt="性教育" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sex_Education_Season_4_Ncuti_Gatwa.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sex_Education_Season_4_Ncuti_Gatwa-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sex_Education_Season_4_Ncuti_Gatwa-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sex_Education_Season_4_Ncuti_Gatwa-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sex_Education_Season_4_Ncuti_Gatwa-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sex_Education_Season_4_Ncuti_Gatwa-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3501198" class="wp-caption-text">恩库蒂·盖特瓦在《性教育》中。图片来源：Netflix</figcaption></figure><p>正如<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/sex-education-confirmed-to-end-season-four-watch-first-trailer-3465160">7 月份的公告中所详述的</a>那样，主创劳里·纳恩 (Laurie Nunn) 表示， <em>《性爱自修室》</em>的故事情节在编写第四季时就自然而然地得出了结论。</p><p> “写这篇文章感觉苦乐参半，因为我们决定第四季也将是我们节目的最后一部分，”纳恩说。 “这不是一个容易做出的决定，但随着新一季的主题和故事的具体化，很明显这是毕业的正确时机。”</p><p>她补充道：“我们对<em>《性教育》</em>感到无比自豪，并感谢我们出色的编剧、演员和工作人员，他们为制作每一集付出了如此多的心血。他们孜孜不倦地为您带来最后一季，我们迫不及待地想与您分享。告别是最糟糕的，但让我们庆祝我们度过的所有美好时光。”</p><p>然而，纳恩在接受<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2023/sep/16/sex-education-laurie-nunn-netflix-final-series" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《卫报》</em></a>采访时表示，该剧的结局是有意不“完全完美地结束”。</p><p> “我认为，如果你在开始写作时考虑人们对作品的反应，它可能会变得非常不自然，”她说。</p><p> “我希望[结局]有一种苦乐参半的感觉，并且里面有人们想要的一切，尽管它可能没有完全完美地结束。”</p><h2>可能会有分拆吗？ </h2><figure id="attachment_3499930" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3499930" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3499930" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sex-Education-season-4-asa-butterfield.jpg" alt="性教育第四季" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sex-Education-season-4-asa-butterfield.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sex-Education-season-4-asa-butterfield-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sex-Education-season-4-asa-butterfield-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sex-Education-season-4-asa-butterfield-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sex-Education-season-4-asa-butterfield-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Sex-Education-season-4-asa-butterfield-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3499930" class="wp-caption-text">阿萨·巴特菲尔德在《性教育》第四季中。图片来源：Netflix</figcaption></figure><p>在接受<em><a href="https://www.netflix.com/tudum/articles/sex-education-season-4-final-release-date-cast-photos-news" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Tudum</a></em>采访时，纳恩调侃<em>《性教育》</em>世界中的角色“总是有更多的潜力”。</p><p> “我肯定会休息一下并考虑其他事情，”纳恩说。 “但是穆尔代尔是一个非常丰富的世界，写青少年的故事总是很有趣。所以，我认为这个世界总是有更多值得探索的潜力。”</p><p>随着许多核心演员转向其他项目，下一步可能是推出新剧组的衍生剧，或者专注于被忽视的角色。</p><p> <em>《性教育》</em>可在 Netflix 上观看。</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/why-is-sex-education-ending-netflix-3501275">为什么“性教育”结束了？</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
