-from-touring-and-cancels-all-remaining-shows-3390301">宣布退出巡演</a>，并取消了原定的欧洲和英国巡演日期。然而，当月晚些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ozzy-osbourne-says-he-would-tour-again-weeks-after-announcing-his-retirement-3406010">他表示希望在未来的某个时候重返舞台</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ozzy-osbourne-undergoes-final-surgery-i-cant-do-it-anymore-3501571">奥兹·奥斯本接受“最后”手术后的帖子：“我不能再这样做了”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
